  VeeC(A,A) = Coulomb Part of Vee(A,A)
  VeeX(A,A) = Exchange-Correlation Part of Vee(A,A)
  Vee(A,A')/2 = Half of Two-electron Interaction Energy Between Atom A and Other Atoms of Molecule
              = Vee(A) - Vee(A,A)
  VeeC(A,A')/2 = Coulomb Part of Vee(A,A')/2
  VeeX(A,A')/2 = Exchange-Correlation Part of Vee(A,A')/2
